Text: Many of my fav. songs here but Rod Stewart?  Are they any good, Michael? - reviewers seem poles apart.
Sorry, just saw your 'a fine job' comment - I'll trust your judgement.  Thanks.

thank you for your trust in me, I can only say you would likely have to pick and choose even here - it is not normally what is Rod Stewart's usual repertoire as we have known it to be - however on the whole, its certainly a worthwhile collection of nice songs in here along the way- thanks indeed!
Very nice upload, thank you very much
